snippet.title: Tribes of Midgard - Giants Are Coming Trailer | PS5, PS4
snippet.description: Giants Are Coming! Prepare vikings, on July 27 Tribes of Midgard will launch on PlayStation 5 and PlayStation 4. Pre-order now to be among the first to defend the seeds of Yggdrasil in this 10-player co-op action survival RPG developed by Norsfell and published by Gearbox Publishing.
